ndardisierung der Tastuntersuchung des Beckenbodens Objektive Beurteilung einer muskulären Beckenbodenschwäche Festlegung von Behandlungszielen Viele farbige Abbildungen und Merksätze in diesem Buch gewährleisten eine gute Umsetzbarkeit der gezeigten Methode und ihrer Lehre; es ist daher als Kursbuch für Praxis und Unterricht besonders gut geeignet.  aThis book provides information about this rather uncommon technique and lists the indications, applications and advantages of vaginal palpation.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access. Unless otherwise specified individually in the content, the work is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives (CC BY-NC-ND) license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/3.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Feb 2021) 0aBeckenbodengymnastik. 0aFecal incontinencexExercise therapy. 0aPalpation. 0aPelvic floor. 0aUrinary incontinencexExercise therapy. 0aUrinary stress incontinencexExercise therapy. 4aBeckenboden. 4aGynäkologie. 4aInkontinenz. 4aPhysiotherapie. 4aPrävention. 7aMEDICAL / Gynecology & Obstetrics.2bisacsh  aGynecology.  aIncontinence.  aPalpation.  aPelvic Floor Training.  aPhysiotherapy.  aPrevention.1 aBartosch, Bernhard, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aStelzhammer, Christine, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aUdier, Elisabeth, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z97831107009850 cEPUBz97831103916260 cprintz978311024611740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110246124zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110246124zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/